&lt;General Systems ResearchInc> said it concluded a 15 mln dlr private placement with thegovernment of Alberta.    The provincial government purchased 15 mln dlrs of thecompany's class A preferred shares.    The government of Alberta also converted a 2.5 mln dlrdebenture into common shares and converted about 2.5 mln dlrsof shareholders' loans into common shares, the company said.Conversion price for both transactions was 1.75 dlrs per share. Reuter&#3;